item.title: How do u make ur self admin?
item.dc:creator: @MoparScape_Poster MoparScape Poster
item.description:
@MoparScape_Poster wrote:

If you have your own server up and running the file mostly called Characters, Open that file and you should see your account(s) name in there. You must of loged in before for it to work.

Then open your characters file(named for char.) and look down the list of things, you should see character right: 0.

Change that 0 to a 1 2 or 3.

1 being Moderator
2 being Admin
3 being Owner of server or Co-Owner

This process works when making others rights high such as admin or mod.
